<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);">MAITRE gives research centres and universities located in Europe and <u><a href="ftp://ftp.cordis.europa.eu/pub/fp7/docs/third_country_agreements_en.pdf" target="_blank">Associated countries</a></u> the opportunity to </span><span style="color:#b70000;"><strong>HOST A PROFESSIONAL MEDIA TRAINING</strong></span><br /><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);">for its researchers completely </span><span style="color:#b70000;"><strong>free of charge</strong></span></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><br /><span style="font-size:14px;"><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);">If you are a member of a </span><span style="color:#b70000;"><strong>research centre or university</strong></span><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);">, please contact the </span><u><span style="color:#b70000;"><strong><a href="mailto:maitre@maitreproject.eu" style="color:#b70000;">MAITRE team</a></strong></span></u><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"> </span></span><span style="color: rgb(105, 105, 105);"><span style="font-size:14px;">for more information<br />&nbsp;<br />Don’t miss out on this special opportunity to host a MAITRE media training session<br />and improve the communication skills of your researchers!</span></span><br style="clear:both;" /><br style="clear:both;" /><span style="font-size:12px;"><em>Here is a list of research centres that have hosted a MAITRE seminar in the past</em></span></p>
